Added `Revocation` ObjectFieldsPanel to Advanced Tab in detail JobResult view.
Added `revoke-job` endpoint to terminate a running or pending Job, or reap it if its worker is gone.
Added column `Revocation Type` to JobResult list view to see what kind of revoke type was executed.
Added filter `Revocation Type` to JobResult list view to permit filtering by revocation type Terminated or Reaped.
Added `Revoke Job` button to JobResult detail view to execute revoke action.
